Installation

install jack, sndfile, fftw3, scons

sonotopy (https://github.com/alex-berman/sonotopy)
	git clone https://github.com/alex-berman/sonotopy.git
	cd sonotopy
	scons
	sudo scons install

	compile in 32-bit on OS X:

	scons CCFLAGS="-arch i386"
	sudo scons CCFLAGS="-arch i386" install

echoprint-codegen
	install boost, taglib, ffmpeg
	(OS X: sudo port install boost taglib ffmpeg)

	git clone https://github.com/gaborpapp/echoprint-codegen.git
	cd echoprint-codegen/src
	make
	sudo make install

pyechonest (http://code.google.com/p/pyechonest/)
	download http://pyechonest.googlecode.com/files/pyechonest.zip
	python setup.py build
	sudo python setup.py install

android track id:
	install android sdk
	install tesseract, imagemagick
	(OS X: sudo port install tesseract ImageMagick)
	put android-sdk/tools on path
	disable locking on phone
	disable landscape orientation on phone
	disable incoming calls

